A button that appears in your Message Context Menu, this reports a message for Potential Usage of AI and logs it to the Logs Channel.

If the message is indeed AI generated, it'll be removed and be asked to never do it again.

Spamming the usage of this button will get you a harsh punishment, so do not actually do it.

## Arguments:
Warn AI Usage does not have any arguments, just hover the message, and click, that's it.

## Example Usage:
```
> *Message has potential use of AI...*
> >Warn AI Usage
>> Potential Reporting has been Logged.
```